Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it'll be spring soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third term will be \Nover before we know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so? It felt incredibly long to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the only days you attended school
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are that day with the whole fuss \Nabout Miss Katsura possibly quitting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.99,0:00:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the episode that \Naired before this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm technically the main heroine,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't ditch in an episode \Ncentered on Hakuou Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again with that nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're leaving, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. School is just such a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'd be a different story if this \Nwere Hourai Academy or Cromartie High.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'd love to wear the \NAshford Academy's uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}The Miss's dislike for school \Ncertainly is a problem... {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:00:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, if it isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hayata and Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What might you ladies be up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought we would participate \Nin some club activities for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I had totally assumed that you \Nall belonged to the "Go Home" Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curious, Hayata?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No, not especially...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? You'd love to come observe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come drop by the club room!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, w-wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Just as we'd planned. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Do you know, ladies and gentlemen? {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}That a humongous mansion like \Nthis exists somewhere in Tokyo? {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}The Miss's name is Nagi Sanzenin. And... {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Her butler's name is Hayate Ayasaki. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}They are both a bit clueless {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}and both have a bit of the \Nwrong idea about each other, {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}but they share the immensely strong, loving \Nbond between servant and mistress. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a story from when Smiley-Smiley \Nwere still able to fly in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:04.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\N I don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:07.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai! \NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\N The future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:18.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honne o misecha make datoka \NStuff like, showing your true feelings means defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:23.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentaku hajiku jinsei datoka\N Or a life tapping away at a calculator
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:28.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro o itsuwaru kurai nara\N Rather than be false to myself like that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichiten-battou baka-shoujiki mo kuuzen-zetsugo! \NI'll struggle to be uniquely naïve and honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Komatta kao o mireba ki-ni-naru shi\N If I see a troubled look, I'll be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:44.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinsei isogu riyuu mo betsuni nai shi \NAnd it's not like I've got a reason to hurry through life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:50.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu wa kimi ni azukeyou \NI'll entrust you with the treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:56.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin yori-michi datte tsukiau yo! \NI'll even keep you company on your free-ranging detours
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkii-sugiru tenkai \NA development that's way too lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae wa mayowanai \NI won't hesitate to give my answer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:07.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kantan sa! Subete wa kimi no tame ni \NIt's easy! It's all for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuhyou wa ki-ni-shinai \NI won't worry about the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rettou-kan ni doujinai!\N I won't let a sense of inferiority get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakedasu shunkan wa ima koko ni aru \NThe moment to start running is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ordinary Stories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Society for the Research of Video?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:45.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Society for the Research of Video
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, this is an awfully \Ndistinctive club house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This building was apparently designed \Nto the tastes of our founding senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is 16mm film!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(194,79)}Illustrative Clip
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is a super-HARP camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this is a film society!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A society for the research of film!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got no interest \Nwhatsoever in making films.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do difficult things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We record and collect interesting and \Nfunny videos, both past and present,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and burst out laughing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} is what we do here,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,always smiley-smiley Society \Nfor the Research of Video!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For short, we call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}YouTuubee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YouTuubee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For short?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it is a "Killing Time" Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Who are you accusing of killing time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Society for the Research of Video, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds a bit interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}What?! U-Unbelievable! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}The Miss is taking an interest in \Nhaving dealings with other people! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}No, isn't she taking an interest in videos? {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, are you \Ninvolved in any clubs, Little Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, nothing especially right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Then why don't you give this a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our club was originally formed \Nto make videos of cute girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's an easygoing club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll at least serve to make some memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, what should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Th-This is an opportunity! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}The Miss tends to socially withdrawn, {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}so this is a unique chance to have \Nher enjoy a proper school life! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}How could I call myself a butler \Nif I do not encourage this?! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}All right! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that sounds {\i1}very{\i0} interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? So? What kind of videos \Ndo you make, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our projects are just \Nkind of scattered over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then let us watch some of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, you said you \Nmade videos of cute girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, I'm Hayako Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a slightly mischievous 16-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, someone wonderful, come \Ntake Hayako on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That was a great project!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing secretly taping me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.83,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you even dubbed dialogue over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that? It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, we have cameras \Nset up all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the top of Mount Everest to Shizuka's \Nbathing room at the Minamoto residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No filming! {\i1}No{\i0} filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Makimura, I... I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't, Ayasaki. You and \NI are student and teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I want to stay like \Nthis forever with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb jerk! Don't make trouble for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Havin' affairs shows what a man's made of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women provide fodder for the arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes it look like I'm some \Nterribly licentious "sensualist"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate, what was that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're accidents! Every single \None of them was by complete accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us excuse ourselves now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're leaving, Hayata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.74,0:07:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being shown any more strange \Nvideos is more than I can bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Help you? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.94,0:07:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be having fun, my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Superintendent! Wh-What \Nare you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Onsite Club Inspection Day, \Nwhich Mistress Kuzuha conducts herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Onsite inspection?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I check to make sure no one is deviating \Nfrom what students should be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.54,0:07:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I guess she does some \Nserious work once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not be fooled, Hayata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way she's doing serious work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea how the students have \Nsuffered because of these onsite inspections!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, the tennis team...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even have a lethal technique \Non the order of a Boomerang Snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the American football team...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't even do the Sky Devil Bat Dive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the Puppeteering Club...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.14,0:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I have come to save you, princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will you wind? Or not wind?" is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.66,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're not windup dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Come, let us go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, countless clubs have been shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna get shut down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why we were plotting \Nto invite into our club
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the superintendent's favorite guys, \Nwhich is to say, you, Hayata,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and furthermore, to show her \Nnumerous seductive videos of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which would strike a chord \Nwith the superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but there's no way the superintendent \Nwould enjoy seeing such...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This was candid video of Hayate Ayasaki \Nin delightfully embarrassing situations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could've seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally wish I could've seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress Kuzuha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I order the Society for the Research \Nof Video to be disbanded at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, you will be the \NSociety for the Research of Ono no Imoko
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or the Society for the Research of \NEating Udon Noodles Through Your Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least make \Nit a more normal club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man, and we were about to \Nmake the best video of all, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The best video of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were planning on showing \Nit to you, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.56,0:09:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of video was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.48,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A collection of end credit bloopers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End credit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know all those Jackie films?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how his films show \Nbloopers during the end credits?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those things"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say I think \NJackie's not bad myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Unbelievable! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}The Miss is showing interest in \Nsomething that is not 2-dimensional! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}As a butler, I absolutely must \Ndo this for my mistress! {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to back out, now's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can miss this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think it might be \Nbetter if he didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, here I go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So will Jackie do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly, Jackie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Meanwhile, right around the same time... {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Makimura, you can't \Nvideotape stuff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! I said, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined such old \Nfootage would surface again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}In the world of the internet, {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}it is difficult to recover video \Nthat has once been circulated. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Be careful with that. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love you, okay? Sheesh.\N({\u1}Su{\u0}-Sukinanda kara, mo{\u1}u{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm crying because I'm happy, you moron!\N({\u1}U{\u0}reshi-naki ja, bo{\u1}ke{\u0}!)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First Hakuou Academy Society \Nfor the Research of Video...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Fun-Fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Ordinary Story Championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...title says it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the Society for the Research of \NVideo, safety really comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have decided to return \Nto our original purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make videos that the entire family \Ncan enjoy in their living rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After everything we've been through, \Nwe won't let you back out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We entered into a secret agreement \Nwith the superintendent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that if we submit a funny \Nvideo with you in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.14,0:11:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll triple our budget for the next term!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Little Nagi's given her consent \Nto cooperate as a member of the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is this Ordinary Story Championship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good of you to ask, Nagi-pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Nagi-rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is what it's about, Nagi Springfield!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um, won't you please address \Nme normally as "Nagi"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened when I was back in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to this one shabby fishing \Nvillage in the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if time had \Nstopped in this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a pretty spooky place to begin with,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but at the bed and breakfast where \Nwe stayed, there was even...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a crumbling statue of Kinjiro \NNinomiya facing the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the proprietress \Nof the bed and breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, at night, that statue \Nturns around to glare behind him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make sure none of the children \Nstaying at the inn are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you must never stay up late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've heard of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you're going to \Ncollect these common stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where the story gets good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard that, it made me want \Nto see if it was true, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So a bunch of us kids snuck out \Nin the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was truly the dead of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even thinking back now, I \Nwish we hadn't gone, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the weather was bad, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind sounded like people moaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We waited for 10 minutes, then 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was summer, but oddly chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And suddenly, we looked around \Nand we couldn't believe our eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we knew it, we'd fallen \Nasleep and morning had come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about the Kinjiro statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were all asleep, \Nso we weren't able to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a worthless story! And you \Nspent roughly 17 scenes telling it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we're going to collect stories like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where only ordinary things happen \Nthat aren't worth telling about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we want to collect videos \Nthat'll make you think,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Aw, man, that sure was a waste of time!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need for such videos!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone's got a worthless \Nstory or two like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now. Are you sure \Nyou don't have one, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A worthless story that you have tucked away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...used to live in a really rundown \Nhouse when I was little, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a story?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This house was really truly rundown
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the windows always rattled at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One night, I was at home alone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and back then, our electricity had \Nbeen stopped, so it was pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to get in my futon and go to sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I suddenly realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That strangely, the rattling sound \Nwas louder than usual somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've been scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I went to the window, as if \NI was drawn there by something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gently drew the curtain aside and \Nslowly looked out the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the wind was blowing harder than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.75,0:14:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is precisely what \Nwe were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Hayata! That was a good story!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me, me! I wanna tell a story, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Katsura! Where did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how I'm not in the \Nnight duty room during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, after work, I suddenly \Nfelt it the moment I went inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "Oh, something's strange."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a glance, nothing had changed \Nin the room, but I could tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That something important was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.39,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched my room thoroughly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I finally figured out what was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.43,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that my wallet was completely empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a 500 million percent certainty, \Nthat's because you spent it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The mic...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I may be so bold, I think I will \Nhave you listen to my story as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus?! Um, this is our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it has come to this, I will \Nappear in any scene I can get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.31,0:15:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time at the Sanzenin residence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we had a dog named Lucky \Nrunning loose in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we had \Na stupid dog like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He certainly was a stupid dog,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but well, by around 6 in the evening, he \Nwould always be back in his hut, sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:01.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But one day, evening came \Nand he had not returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(365,251)}Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was left running loose, but he did \Nnot appear to have left the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no matter how stupid he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it seemed unlikely that he \Nhad gotten lost in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked for Lucky all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was nowhere to be \Nfound and a day passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a second day passed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky did not return to his hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, on the third day, unbelievably, \NLucky was back in his hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that was the end of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Lucky \Nduring those three days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, could I try telling a story, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were cleaning up around the house \Nwhen Kotetsu found an old wooden box.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievably, what we found inside
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the withered mummified \Nhand of a water imp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there were words carved into \Nthe back of the wooden box.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said that this hand would \Ngrant its owner any 3 wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Did you make any wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! There's bound \Nto be a terrible curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, unbelievably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we put it out with the \Nunburnable trash the next day!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't a water imp's \Nhand be burnable trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.76,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorting and collection of \Ntrash differs by region.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is right. It is burnable trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Your local municipality will \Nhave the information, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. That was careless of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:25.04,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, there has been a lot of \Ntrash that has been sorted wrongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:26.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure to properly sort burnable \Ntrash, unburnable trash, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's turned into an ordinary \Ndiscussion of trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.34,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,and put it out on time on the day of \Ncollection in the trash collection area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I am next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with \Nthe term "doppelganger"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This refers to a phenomenon where you bump \Ninto someone who looks exactly like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that those who see their \Ndoppelganger will die soon thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, Lincoln also saw his \Nthe day before he was assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese poet Murou Saisei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He also had just such a doppelganger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is sounding rather like an urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think "Murou Saisei" sounds just \Nlike "slow saisei (slow motion replay)"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.42,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"toudai motokurashi\N(the darkest place is under the candlestick)"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, "toudai motokurashi" and "Taisho \Ndemocracy" are exactly alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And also "Jurassic Park" and "Juraku \Nni nisan-paku (2-3 nights at Juraku)".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is more like a meaningless \Nstory than an ordinary one...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you believe or not is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would like, I could tell \Na story about my family home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Saki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My family home was rundown
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the stairs creaked \Nwhenever one of us used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, the entire family \Nwas having dinner downstairs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we heard the familiar \Nnoise from the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, my mother said, "Our home really \Nhas become rundown, hasn't it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she had it remodeled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what an ordinary story that was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been listening for a while now and \Nyou've been telling some boring stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was wondering who \Nhad come, but you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Club President! You're our club president!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Club president?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy is none other than
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the current president of the Society for \Nthe Research of Video, Wataru Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, they just made me their \Npresident without asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.56,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have you know, our \Npresident is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He makes anime MAD openings that \Nordinary people would think were real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the "guy voice" videos were \Nmade by the president, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get down to it, all your stories \Nare just left hanging there with no punch line.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our president for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you can tell a \Nfunny story that has a punch line?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I'm saying is that I want an ordinary \Nstory that touches the heart more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ordinary story that touches the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is about the universe, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that the universe is expanding \Nat an incredible rate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, you also know that light's \Nthe fastest thing in the universe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's common knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the universe's rate of expansion gets \Nfaster the farther it is from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the farther a star is from \NEarth, the faster it's moving away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally, impossibly, those \Nstars surpass the speed of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.06,0:20:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that fascinating?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-President...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that's the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Thus, they say an incredibly \Nmeaningless day ended. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish something nice would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A p-peach?! What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reach it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Since I can't reach it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy a can of peaches on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring-a-ding. Ring-a-ding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}And here was yet another ordinary story. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Next time, they will fight against \Na neighborhood quiz contest. {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.25,0:21:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're in front of Yukiji's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go right ahead and check \Nto see if she's up or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, but before we do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all of you watching "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will probably be the last time \Nthat we will be featured in an episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This and that. Looking back, a lot \Nof things happened, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It puts us in a slightly sentimental mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the end is the start \Nof the end of the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet again someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a one, two... Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Committee Chairman,\N Red Izumi Segawa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come wake me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:36.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Chairman, Blue Miki Hanabishi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rare, I tell you! Rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Video of me waking up will easily get \N300,000 views and 100,000 comments in one night!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.80,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Disciplinary Committee Member,\N Black Risa Asakaze
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The End
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:07.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaretai fureraretetai\NI want to be loved, to feel that touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Motomeru bakari no kimochi wa\NThe sense of continually seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.05,0:22:15.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibi o kumoraseteta\NUsed to darken my days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:23.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ni deau sono hi made wa\NUntil the day I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:33.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde sora ni hibiku-youni\NCall my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:43.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi-michi mo kitto futari nara\NEven lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:48.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunaida te to te hanasanai\NI won't let go of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoritainda\NI want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.43,0:22:57.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saa ikou bokura wa\NCome on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:09.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima o mitsumete aruki-hajimeru\N...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.59,0:23:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(437,45)}17-year-old Maria's Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:29.37,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,288)}Lettering by Rie Tanaka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and 17-year-old Maria's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.40,0:23:31.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pakkyuruun, I'm Nagi Sanzenin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Maria, 17 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The days have been cold, but \NI hope you've been well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's cold like this, it's best \Nnot to force yourself to go out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to immerse yourself \Nin online games at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, you won't become a \Nmaster at living life like Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my, Hayate. But I'm only a \Nyear older than you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, pardon me, but you're so mature. \NEven kind of middle-aged...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.48,0:23:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, here's today's fan service shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.62,0:23:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue to give your support \Nto "Hayate the Combat Butler".
