Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.64,0:24:19.67,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:05.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Your hosts will be myself, Teruo Mikiri... {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.16,0:24:07.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Demonking Abe, tima!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:10.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The participating duos will be 10,000 pairs of \Ngirls who have gathered from all across the country, tima!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:13.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Now, which pair will win \Nthe crown of victory? {\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:14.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait, tima!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.33,0:24:17.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Quiz! Written as \N'Foe' and Read as 'Friend'!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.26,0:24:19.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to end up \Nin this with the hamster?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.70,0:24:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiz! Written as "Foe" and Read as "Friend"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.98,0:24:22.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again, next time on "Hayate the Combat \NButler", we'll be doing... the straining pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.84,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the surge!
